HeraPy is a Python package for AERGO that provides the features below.


Features
--------

* Communication with a node
* Getting a metadata
* Managing an account
* Making and sending a transaction
* Making and sending a smart contract

Install
-------

.. code-block:: console

   pip install aergo-herapy


